title: The Largest Hacker Botnet Just Got Taken Down...
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at "Qakbot", a strain of malware that caused a botnet of over 700,000 strong that caused a lot of mayhem since the mid-2000s. How did they finally get caught up by authorities? Let's find out! Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!

Check out the newest podcast episode: https://youtu.be/VlAZEsqtWQE
